# The filing archive. Large, binary, and grows forever.
#
# NOTE: this is the project's most valuable asset and it CANNOT be rebuilt --
# Companies House purges daily files after 60 days and TDnet after ~30. Keep it
# out of git, but back it up somewhere durable. See PLAN.md section 1.3.
data/
!data/.gitkeep

